Module com.example.cs213_cafe_project
Package com.example.cs213_cafe_project

Class OrderCoffeeController

java.lang.Object
com.example.cs213_cafe_project.OrderCoffeeController
public class OrderCoffeeController extends Object
Controller class for orderingCoffee.fxml Does all the event handling and the action handling for the coffee view. Sends and receives data with the mainController.

    • fillSet

      private void fillSet(HashSet<AddOn> addOnList, boolean sweetCream, boolean mocha, boolean frenchVanilla, boolean caramel, boolean irishCream)
      Fills the provided set with addOn enum Objects based on the boolean values provided. if a checkbox is checked it will feed true to this function.
      Parameters:
      addOnList - HashSet that will hold all the addOns for our coffee Object.
      sweetCream - boolean checkBox checked. true if check, false otherwise
      mocha - boolean checkBox checked. true if check, false otherwise
      frenchVanilla - boolean checkBox checked. true if check, false otherwise
      caramel - boolean checkBox checked. true if check, false otherwise
      irishCream - boolean checkBox checked. true if check, false otherwise
